title: You, too, should feel free to add a 'PROPERTIES' bucket with an ID to anything in my graph that you want to reference.
pid: 54af9acc-8056-4584-9fca-3bbc94ae6716
body: |2-
  I'm still not ready for you to edit it in other ways, though, so at least for now please keep all your creations in by-claude/.
